# ШЈЩҲШ§Щ…Шұ ШҘШ¶Ш§ЩҒЩҠШ© Щ„ЩҒШ§ЩҶШӘШІЩҠ Ш§Щ„Щ…ШөЩҠЩҒ
# ШЈШ¶ЩҒ ЩҮШ°Ш§ Ш§Щ„ЩӮШіЩ… ЩӮШЁЩ„: async def dashboard
# ============================================================

PENDING_IMPORTS = {}
LAST_UPLOADED_FILES = {}
INVALID_SELECTIONS_GLOBAL = {"", "Щ„Щ… ЩҠШҙШ§ШұЩғ", "ШӘЩ… ШӯШ¬ШЁ Ш§Щ„Щ…ШҙШ§ШұЩғШ© / ШӘШЈШ®ЩҠШұ"}

# Ш§ШіШӘШЁШҜЩ„ ШҜШ§Щ„Ш© is_no_participation Ш§Щ„ЩӮШҜЩҠЩ…Ш© ШЁЩҮШ°Ш§ Ш§Щ„ШӘШ№ШұЩҠЩҒ
# ШЈЩҲ Ш§ШӘШұЩғ ЩҮШ°Ш§ Ш§Щ„ШӘШ№ШұЩҠЩҒ ШЁШ№ШҜ Ш§Щ„ЩӮШҜЩҠЩ…Ш© Ш№ШҙШ§ЩҶ ЩҠШәШ·ЩҠЩҮШ§.
def is_no_participation(value):
    value = normalize_name(value)
    return value in INVALID_SELECTIONS_GLOBAL


def load_workbook_safely(path, data_only=True):
    """ЩҠЩҒШӘШӯ Щ…Щ„ЩҒШ§ШӘ Ш§Щ„ШҘЩғШіЩ„ ШӯШӘЩү Щ„ЩҲ ЩҒЩҠЩҮШ§ Щ…ШҙЩғЩ„Ш© styles Щ…Ш«Щ„ family val > 14."""
    import zipfile
    import tempfile
    import re as _re

    try:
        return load_workbook(path, data_only=data_only)
    except Exception:
        fixed_path = os.path.join(tempfile.gettempdir(), f"fixed_{os.path.basename(path)}")
        with zipfile.ZipFile(path, "r") as zin, zipfile.ZipFile(fixed_path, "w", zipfile.ZIP_DEFLATED) as zout:
            for item in zin.infolist():
                data = zin.read(item.filename)
                if item.filename == "xl/styles.xml":
                    text = data.decode("utf-8", errors="ignore")
                    text = _re.sub(r'<family val="(?:1[5-9]|[2-9][0-9]+)"\s*/>', '<family val="2"/>', text)
                    data = text.encode("utf-8")
                zout.writestr(item, data)
        return load_workbook(fixed_path, data_only=data_only)


def cell_text(value):
    return normalize_name(value)


def cell_int(value, default=0):
    try:
        if value is None or value == "":
            return default
        return int(float(value))
    except Exception:
        return default


def parse_import_excel(path):
    """
    ЩҠШіШӘЩҲШұШҜ Щ…Щ„ЩҒ Ш§Щ„ШҘЩғШіЩ„ ЩғШ§Щ…Щ„ Щ…ШұШ© ЩҲШӯШҜШ©.
    ЩҠШҜШ№Щ… ШөЩҒШӯШ§ШӘ ШЁШ§ШіЩ…: ЩҠЩҲЩ… 1ШҢ ЩҠЩҲЩ… 2ШҢ ...
    ЩҲЩҠШіШӯШЁ:
    - Ш¬ШҜЩҲЩ„ Ш§Щ„ЩҶШӘШ§ШҰШ¬ Щ…ЩҶ Ш§Щ„ШЈШ№Щ…ШҜШ© A:B:C
    - Ш¬ШҜЩҲЩ„ Ш§Щ„Щ…ШҙШ§ШұЩғЩҠЩҶ Щ…ЩҶ Ш№ЩҶШҜ Ш№Щ…ЩҲШҜ "Ш§Щ„Щ…ШҙШ§ШұЩғ"
    ЩҲЩҠШӘШ¬Ш§ЩҮЩ„ Ш§Щ„ШЈЩҠШ§Щ… Ш§Щ„ЩҒШ§Ш¶ЩҠШ© ШЁШ§Щ„ЩғШ§Щ…Щ„ ШӯШӘЩү Щ„Ш§ ЩҠЩҶШҙШҰ ШЈЩҠШ§Щ… ЩҲЩҮЩ…ЩҠШ©.
    """
    wb = load_workbook_safely(path, data_only=True)
    imported = {}

    TRUE_VALUES = {"ЩҶШ№Щ…", "yes", "Yes", "YES", "ШөШӯ", "вң“", "вң…", "1", "true", "True"}

    for ws in wb.worksheets:
        m = re.search(r"ЩҠЩҲЩ…\s*(\d+)", str(ws.title))
        if not m:
            continue

        day = int(m.group(1))

        # ЩҶШЁШӯШ« Ш№ЩҶ Ш®Ш§ЩҶШ© "Ш§Щ„Щ…ШҙШ§ШұЩғ" ЩҒЩҠ ШЈЩҲЩ„ Ш§Щ„ШөЩҒЩҲЩҒ
        header_row = None
        participant_col = None
        for r in range(1, min(ws.max_row, 25) + 1):
            for c in range(1, min(ws.max_column, 25) + 1):
                if cell_text(ws.cell(r, c).value) == "Ш§Щ„Щ…ШҙШ§ШұЩғ":
                    header_row = r
                    participant_col = c
                    break
            if header_row:
                break

        if not header_row or not participant_col:
            continue

        lineups = {}
        active_found = False

        # Ш§Щ„Щ…ШҙШ§ШұЩғЩҲЩҶ: Ш§Щ„Щ…ШҙШ§ШұЩғШҢ Ш§Щ„ШӯШ§ШұШіШҢ Ш§Щ„Щ„Ш§Ш№ШЁ 1ШҢ Ш§Щ„Щ„Ш§Ш№ШЁ 2ШҢ Ш§Щ„Щ„Ш§Ш№ШЁ 3ШҢ Ш§Щ„ЩғШ§ШЁШӘЩҶ
        for r in range(header_row + 1, ws.max_row + 1):
            participant = cell_text(ws.cell(r, participant_col).value)
            if not participant or participant not in PARTICIPANTS:
                continue

            values = [cell_text(ws.cell(r, participant_col + offset).value) for offset in range(1, 6)]

            # Щ„ЩҲ Ш§Щ„ШөЩҒ ЩҒШ§Ш¶ЩҠ ШЈЩҲ ЩғЩ„ЩҮ Ш№ШҜЩ… Щ…ШҙШ§ШұЩғШ©
            if all(is_no_participation(v) for v in values):
                values = ["Щ„Щ… ЩҠШҙШ§ШұЩғ"] * 5
            else:
                active_found = True

            lineups[participant] = values

        # Ш§Щ„ЩҶШӘШ§ШҰШ¬: ШәШ§Щ„ШЁЩӢШ§ ЩҒЩҠ A:B:C = Ш§ШіЩ… Ш§Щ„Щ„Ш§Ш№ШЁ | Ш№ШҜШҜ Ш§Щ„ШЈЩҮШҜШ§ЩҒ | ЩғЩ„ЩҠЩҶ ШҙЩҠШӘШҹ
        goals_count = defaultdict(int)
        clean_sheets = []

        for r in range(header_row + 1, ws.max_row + 1):
            name = cell_text(ws.cell(r, 1).value)
            goals_raw = ws.cell(r, 2).value
            clean_raw = cell_text(ws.cell(r, 3).value)

            if not name or is_no_participation(name):
                continue

            goals = cell_int(goals_raw, 0)
            if goals > 0:
                goals_count[name] += goals

            if clean_raw in TRUE_VALUES:
                if name not in clean_sheets:
                    clean_sheets.append(name)

        # Щ„Ш§ ЩҶШіШӘЩҲШұШҜ Ш§Щ„ШЈЩҠШ§Щ… Ш§Щ„ЩҒШ§Ш¶ЩҠШ© ШЁШ§Щ„ЩғШ§Щ…Щ„ШҢ Щ…Ш«Щ„ ЩҠЩҲЩ… 7 ЩҲЩ…Ш§ ШЁШ№ШҜЩҮ ШҘШ°Ш§ Щ…Ш§ Ш§ЩҶЩ„Ш№ШЁШӘ
        if not active_found and not goals_count and not clean_sheets:
            continue

        if lineups:
            imported[day] = {
                "lineups": lineups,
                "goals_count": dict(goals_count),
                "clean_sheets": clean_sheets,
            }

    return imported

def import_summary_text(imported):
    lines = ["ШӘЩ… ЩӮШұШ§ШЎШ© Ш§Щ„Щ…Щ„ЩҒ вң…", "", "Ш§Щ„ШЈЩҠШ§Щ… Ш§Щ„Щ…ЩҲШ¬ЩҲШҜШ©:"]
    if not imported:
        lines.append("Щ…Ш§ Щ„ЩӮЩҠШӘ ШЈЩҠШ§Щ… ЩӮШ§ШЁЩ„Ш© Щ„Щ„Ш§ШіШӘЩҠШұШ§ШҜ.")
        return "\n".join(lines)

    for day in sorted(imported):
        data = imported[day]
        participants = len(data["lineups"])
        has_results = bool(data["goals_count"] or data["clean_sheets"])
        status = "ЩҶШӘШ§ШҰШ¬ Щ…ЩҲШ¬ЩҲШҜШ©" if has_results else "ШЁШҜЩҲЩҶ ЩҶШӘШ§ШҰШ¬"
        exists = " вҖ” Щ…ЩҲШ¬ЩҲШҜ Щ…ШіШЁЩӮЩӢШ§ ЩҲШіЩҠШӘЩ… Ш§ШіШӘШЁШҜШ§Щ„ЩҮ" if os.path.exists(excel_file(day)) else ""
        lines.append(f"Ш§Щ„ЩҠЩҲЩ… {day}: {participants} Щ…ШҙШ§ШұЩғ + {status}{exists}")

    lines.append("")
    lines.append("Щ„Щ„Ш§Ш№ШӘЩ…Ш§ШҜ Ш§ЩғШӘШЁ:")
    lines.append("/Ш§Ш№ШӘЩ…Ш§ШҜ_Ш§ШіШӘЩҠШұШ§ШҜ")
    lines.append("")
    lines.append("Щ„Щ„ШҘЩ„ШәШ§ШЎ Ш§ЩғШӘШЁ:")
    lines.append("/ШҘЩ„ШәШ§ШЎ_Ш§ШіШӘЩҠШұШ§ШҜ")
    return "\n".join(lines)


async def _download_document_to_folder(update: Update, context: ContextTypes.DEFAULT_TYPE, folder="uploads"):
    """ЩҠШӯЩҒШё ШЈЩҠ Щ…Щ„ЩҒ Щ…ШұШіЩ„ ЩҲЩҠШұШ¬Ш№ Ш§Щ„Щ…ШіШ§Шұ Ш§Щ„Щ…ШӯЩ„ЩҠ."""
    document = update.message.document
    if not document:
        return None, None

    filename = document.file_name or "uploaded_file"
    os.makedirs(folder, exist_ok=True)
    safe_name = re.sub(r"[^A-Za-z0-9_.\-\u0600-\u06FF]+", "_", filename)
    local_path = os.path.join(folder, f"{update.effective_chat.id}_{datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d_%H%M%S')}_{safe_name}")

    tg_file = await context.bot.get_file(document.file_id)
    await tg_file.download_to_drive(local_path)
    return local_path, filename


async def remember_last_file(update: Update, context: ContextTypes.DEFAULT_TYPE):
    """ЩҠШӯЩҒШё ШўШ®Шұ Щ…Щ„ЩҒ Excel ШЈЩҲ ZIP ШЈШұШіЩ„ЩҮ Ш§Щ„Щ…ШіШӘШ®ШҜЩ…ШҢ Ш№ШҙШ§ЩҶ ЩҶЩӮШҜШұ ЩҶШіШӘШ®ШҜЩ…ЩҮ ШЁШ№ШҜЩҠЩҶ ШЁШҜЩҲЩҶ ШӘШ№Щ„ЩҠЩӮ."""
    local_path, filename = await _download_document_to_folder(update, context, "uploads")
    if not local_path:
        return

    chat_id = update.effective_chat.id
    LAST_UPLOADED_FILES.setdefault(chat_id, {})
    lower = (filename or "").lower()
    caption = (update.message.caption or "").strip()

    if lower.endswith((".xlsx", ".xlsm")):
        LAST_UPLOADED_FILES[chat_id]["excel"] = local_path
        if caption.startswith("/Ш§ШіШӘЩҠШұШ§ШҜ_Щ…Щ„ЩҒ"):
            await _run_import_from_path(update, context, local_path)
        else:
            await update.message.reply_text(
                "ЩҲШөЩ„ Щ…Щ„ЩҒ Ш§Щ„ШҘЩғШіЩ„ вң…\n"
                "Ш§ЩғШӘШЁ Ш§Щ„ШўЩҶ:\n"
                "/Ш§ШіШӘЩҠШұШ§ШҜ_Щ…Щ„ЩҒ"
            )
        return

    if lower.endswith(".zip"):
        LAST_UPLOADED_FILES[chat_id]["zip"] = local_path
        if caption.startswith("/Ш§ШіШӘШұШ¬Ш§Ш№_ЩҶШіШ®Ш©"):
            await _run_restore_from_zip_path(update, context, local_path)
        else:
            await update.message.reply_text(
                "ЩҲШөЩ„ Щ…Щ„ЩҒ ZIP вң…\n"
                "Щ„Щ„Ш§ШіШӘШұШ¬Ш§Ш№ Ш§ЩғШӘШЁ Ш§Щ„ШўЩҶ:\n"
                "/Ш§ШіШӘШұШ¬Ш§Ш№_ЩҶШіШ®Ш©"
            )
        return

    await update.message.reply_text("ЩҲШөЩ„ Ш§Щ„Щ…Щ„ЩҒШҢ Щ„ЩғЩҶ ШЈШӯШӘШ§Ш¬ Excel ШЈЩҲ ZIP ЩҒЩӮШ·.")


async def _run_import_from_path(update: Update, context: ContextTypes.DEFAULT_TYPE, local_path):
    try:
        imported = parse_import_excel(local_path)
    except Exception as e:
        await update.message.reply_text(f"ШөШ§Шұ Ш®Ш·ШЈ ШЈШ«ЩҶШ§ШЎ ЩӮШұШ§ШЎШ© Ш§Щ„ШҘЩғШіЩ„ вқҢ\n{e}")
        return

    if not imported:
        await update.message.reply_text("Щ…Ш§ ЩӮШҜШұШӘ ШЈШіШӘШ®ШұШ¬ ШЈЩҠШ§Щ… Щ…ЩҶ Ш§Щ„Щ…Щ„ЩҒ. ШӘШЈЩғШҜ ШЈЩҶ Ш§Щ„ШөЩҒШӯШ§ШӘ ШЁШ§ШіЩ…: ЩҠЩҲЩ… 1ШҢ ЩҠЩҲЩ… 2 ...")
        return

    chat_id = update.effective_chat.id
    PENDING_IMPORTS[chat_id] = {"path": local_path, "data": imported}
    await update.message.reply_text(import_summary_text(imported))


async def import_excel_file(update: Update, context: ContextTypes.DEFAULT_TYPE):
    """
    ЩҠШҜШ№Щ… Ш·ШұЩҠЩӮШӘЩҠЩҶ:
    1) ШҘШұШіШ§Щ„ Щ…Щ„ЩҒ Ш§Щ„ШҘЩғШіЩ„ ШЁШӘШ№Щ„ЩҠЩӮ /Ш§ШіШӘЩҠШұШ§ШҜ_Щ…Щ„ЩҒ
    2) ШҘШұШіШ§Щ„ Щ…Щ„ЩҒ Ш§Щ„ШҘЩғШіЩ„ Щ„ШӯШ§Щ„ЩҮШҢ Ш«Щ… ЩғШӘШ§ШЁШ© /Ш§ШіШӘЩҠШұШ§ШҜ_Щ…Щ„ЩҒ
    """
    document = update.message.document
    chat_id = update.effective_chat.id

    if document:
        filename = document.file_name or "import.xlsx"
        if not filename.lower().endswith((".xlsx", ".xlsm")):
            await update.message.reply_text("Ш§Щ„Щ…Щ„ЩҒ Щ„Ш§ШІЩ… ЩҠЩғЩҲЩҶ Excel ШЁШөЩҠШәШ© .xlsx ШЈЩҲ .xlsm")
            return
        local_path, _ = await _download_document_to_folder(update, context, "imports")
        LAST_UPLOADED_FILES.setdefault(chat_id, {})["excel"] = local_path
        await _run_import_from_path(update, context, local_path)
        return

    local_path = LAST_UPLOADED_FILES.get(chat_id, {}).get("excel")
    if not local_path or not os.path.exists(local_path):
        await update.message.reply_text(
            "Щ…Ш§ Щ„ЩӮЩҠШӘ Щ…Щ„ЩҒ Excel Щ…ШӯЩҒЩҲШё.\n"
            "ШЈШұШіЩ„ Щ…Щ„ЩҒ Ш§Щ„ШҘЩғШіЩ„ Щ„ШӯШ§Щ„ЩҮ ШЈЩҲЩ„ЩӢШ§ШҢ ЩҲШЁШ№ШҜЩҮШ§ Ш§ЩғШӘШЁ:\n"
            "/Ш§ШіШӘЩҠШұШ§ШҜ_Щ…Щ„ЩҒ"
        )
        return

    await _run_import_from_path(update, context, local_path)


async def approve_import(update: Update, context: ContextTypes.DEFAULT_TYPE):
    chat_id = update.effective_chat.id
    pending = PENDING_IMPORTS.get(chat_id)
    if not pending:
        await update.message.reply_text("Щ…Ш§ ЩҒЩҠЩҮ Ш§ШіШӘЩҠШұШ§ШҜ Щ…Ш№Щ„ЩӮ. ШЈШұШіЩ„ Щ…Щ„ЩҒ Ш§Щ„ШҘЩғШіЩ„ Щ…Ш№ /Ш§ШіШӘЩҠШұШ§ШҜ_Щ…Щ„ЩҒ ШЈЩҲЩ„ЩӢШ§.")
        return

    imported = pending["data"]
    files_to_backup = [excel_file(day) for day in imported.keys() if os.path.exists(excel_file(day))]
    if os.path.exists(LOCKED_FILE):
        files_to_backup.append(LOCKED_FILE)
    if files_to_backup:
        backup_files("before_import_excel", files=files_to_backup)

    locked = load_locked_days()
    saved_days = []
    warnings = []

    for day in sorted(imported):
        data = imported[day]
        file_name, missing = update_day_data(str(day), data["lineups"])
        if missing:
            warnings.extend([f"Ш§Щ„ЩҠЩҲЩ… {day}: Щ…ШҙШ§ШұЩғ ШәЩҠШұ Щ…ЩҲШ¬ЩҲШҜ ШЁШ§Щ„ЩӮШ§ШҰЩ…Ш©: {m}" for m in missing])
        calculate_points(str(day), data["goals_count"], data["clean_sheets"])
        locked.add(str(day))
        saved_days.append(day)

    save_locked_days(locked)
    PENDING_IMPORTS.pop(chat_id, None)

    msg = [
        "ШӘЩ… Ш§Ш№ШӘЩ…Ш§ШҜ Ш§Щ„Ш§ШіШӘЩҠШұШ§ШҜ вң…",
        f"Ш§Щ„ШЈЩҠШ§Щ… Ш§Щ„Щ…ШӯЩҒЩҲШёШ©: {', '.join(map(str, saved_days))}",
        "ШӘЩ… ШӯШіШ§ШЁ Ш§Щ„ЩҶШӘШ§ШҰШ¬ ЩҲЩӮЩҒЩ„ Ш§Щ„ШЈЩҠШ§Щ… Ш§Щ„Щ…ШіШӘЩҲШұШҜШ©.",
    ]
    if warnings:
        msg.append("\nШӘЩҶШЁЩҠЩҮШ§ШӘ:")
        msg.extend(warnings[:20])
    await update.message.reply_text("\n".join(msg))


async def cancel_import(update: Update, context: ContextTypes.DEFAULT_TYPE):
    chat_id = update.effective_chat.id
    if chat_id in PENDING_IMPORTS:
        PENDING_IMPORTS.pop(chat_id, None)
        await update.message.reply_text("ШӘЩ… ШҘЩ„ШәШ§ШЎ Ш§Щ„Ш§ШіШӘЩҠШұШ§ШҜ вң…")
    else:
        await update.message.reply_text("Щ…Ш§ ЩҒЩҠЩҮ Ш§ШіШӘЩҠШұШ§ШҜ Щ…Ш№Щ„ЩӮ.")


async def backup_zip(update: Update, context: ContextTypes.DEFAULT_TYPE):
    import zipfile

    files = [f for f in os.listdir(".") if re.match(r"fantasy_day_\d+\.xlsx$", f)]
    if os.path.exists(LOCKED_FILE):
        files.append(LOCKED_FILE)

    if not files:
        await update.message.reply_text("Щ…Ш§ ЩҒЩҠЩҮ Щ…Щ„ЩҒШ§ШӘ ШЈЩҠШ§Щ… Ш№ШҙШ§ЩҶ ШЈШіЩҲЩҠ ЩҶШіШ®Ш© Ш§ШӯШӘЩҠШ§Ш·ЩҠШ©.")
        return

    zip_name = f"fantasy_backup_{datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d_%H%M%S')}.zip"
    with zipfile.ZipFile(zip_name, "w", zipfile.ZIP_DEFLATED) as z:
        for f in sorted(files):
            z.write(f)

    with open(zip_name, "rb") as f:
        await update.message.reply_document(document=f, filename=zip_name, caption="ЩҶШіШ®Ш© Ш§ШӯШӘЩҠШ§Ш·ЩҠШ© Щ„ШЈЩҠШ§Щ… Ш§Щ„ЩҒШ§ЩҶШӘШІЩҠ вң…")


async def _run_restore_from_zip_path(update: Update, context: ContextTypes.DEFAULT_TYPE, local_path):
    import zipfile

    backup_files("before_restore_zip")
    restored = []
    try:
        with zipfile.ZipFile(local_path, "r") as z:
            for name in z.namelist():
                base = os.path.basename(name)
                if re.match(r"fantasy_day_\d+\.xlsx$", base) or base == LOCKED_FILE:
                    with z.open(name) as src, open(base, "wb") as dst:
                        dst.write(src.read())
                    restored.append(base)
    except Exception as e:
        await update.message.reply_text(f"ШөШ§Шұ Ш®Ш·ШЈ ЩҒЩҠ Ш§ШіШӘШұШ¬Ш§Ш№ Ш§Щ„ЩҶШіШ®Ш© вқҢ\n{e}")
        return

    if not restored:
        await update.message.reply_text("Щ…Щ„ЩҒ ZIP Щ…Ш§ ЩҒЩҠЩҮ Щ…Щ„ЩҒШ§ШӘ ШЈЩҠШ§Щ… ШөШ§Щ„ШӯШ©.")
        return

    await update.message.reply_text("ШӘЩ… Ш§ШіШӘШұШ¬Ш§Ш№ Ш§Щ„ЩҶШіШ®Ш© вң…\n" + "\n".join(sorted(restored)))


async def restore_backup_zip(update: Update, context: ContextTypes.DEFAULT_TYPE):
    """ЩҠШҜШ№Щ… ШҘШұШіШ§Щ„ ZIP Щ„ШӯШ§Щ„ЩҮ Ш«Щ… /Ш§ШіШӘШұШ¬Ш§Ш№_ЩҶШіШ®Ш©ШҢ ШЈЩҲ ZIP ШЁШӘШ№Щ„ЩҠЩӮ."""
    document = update.message.document
    chat_id = update.effective_chat.id

    if document:
        filename = document.file_name or "backup.zip"
        if not filename.lower().endswith(".zip"):
            await update.message.reply_text("Ш§Щ„Щ…Щ„ЩҒ Щ„Ш§ШІЩ… ЩҠЩғЩҲЩҶ ZIP.")
            return
        local_path, _ = await _download_document_to_folder(update, context, "restore_uploads")
        LAST_UPLOADED_FILES.setdefault(chat_id, {})["zip"] = local_path
        await _run_restore_from_zip_path(update, context, local_path)
        return

    local_path = LAST_UPLOADED_FILES.get(chat_id, {}).get("zip")
    if not local_path or not os.path.exists(local_path):
        await update.message.reply_text(
            "Щ…Ш§ Щ„ЩӮЩҠШӘ Щ…Щ„ЩҒ ZIP Щ…ШӯЩҒЩҲШё.\n"
            "ШЈШұШіЩ„ Щ…Щ„ЩҒ ZIP Щ„ШӯШ§Щ„ЩҮ ШЈЩҲЩ„ЩӢШ§ШҢ ЩҲШЁШ№ШҜЩҮШ§ Ш§ЩғШӘШЁ:\n"
            "/Ш§ШіШӘШұШ¬Ш§Ш№_ЩҶШіШ®Ш©"
        )
        return

    await _run_restore_from_zip_path(update, context, local_path)


async def clean_days(update: Update, context: ContextTypes.DEFAULT_TYPE):
    """ЩҠЩҶШёЩҒ Ш§Щ„ЩӮЩҒЩ„ Щ…ЩҶ ШЈЩҠШ§Щ… Щ…Ш§ Щ„ЩҮШ§ Щ…Щ„ЩҒ ЩҒШ№Щ„ЩҠ."""
    locked = load_locked_days()
    existing = {str(d) for d in get_existing_days(1, 99)}
    cleaned = {d for d in locked if d in existing}
    removed = sorted(locked - cleaned, key=lambda x: int(x))
    save_locked_days(cleaned)
    if removed:
        await update.message.reply_text("ШӘЩ… ШӘЩҶШёЩҠЩҒ Ш§Щ„ШЈЩҠШ§Щ… Ш§Щ„ЩҲЩҮЩ…ЩҠШ© вң…\nШЈШІЩҠЩ„ШӘ Щ…ЩҶ Ш§Щ„ЩӮЩҒЩ„: " + "ШҢ ".join(removed))
    else:
        await update.message.reply_text("Щ…Ш§ ЩҒЩҠЩҮ ШЈЩҠШ§Щ… ЩҲЩҮЩ…ЩҠШ©. ЩғЩ„ ШҙЩҠШЎ ШӘЩ…Ш§Щ… вң…")



