# ---------- ШӘЩҒШ§ШөЩҠЩ„ Щ…Ш¬Щ…ЩҲШ№Ш© Ш§Щ„Ш®ШөЩ… ----------
def _v38e_ar_to_group_code(ar):
    ar = str(ar or '').strip()
    ar = 'ШЈ' if ar == 'Ш§' else ar
    mp = {v: k for k, v in V33_AR_GROUP_LETTERS.items()}
    return mp.get(ar)


def _v38e_parse_group_part(part):
    s = str(part or '').strip()
    m = re.search(r'(ШЈЩҲЩ„|Ш«Ш§ЩҶЩҠ)\s+Ш§Щ„Щ…Ш¬Щ…ЩҲШ№Ш©\s+([ШЈШ§ШЁШ¬ШҜЩҮЩҖЩҲШІШӯШ·ЩҠЩғЩ„])', s)
    if not m:
        return None, None
    return m.group(1), _v38e_ar_to_group_code(m.group(2))


def _v38e_round32_fixture_info_for_team(team, snap=None):
    snap = snap or _v33_snapshot(False)
    team = _v33_find_team(team) or team
    code, pos, row, rows = _v33_group_row(team, snap)
    try:
        pos = int(pos or 0)
    except Exception:
        pos = 0
    if pos == 3:
        try:
            slot, leader = _v33_third_matchup_line(code, snap)
            return {
                'note': f"Ш«Ш§Щ„Ш« {_v33_group_label(code)} Г— Щ…ШӘШөШҜШұ {_v33_group_label(slot)}" if slot else "ШЈЩҒШ¶Щ„ Ш«Ш§Щ„Ш«",
                'opponent_group': slot,
                'opponent_rank_word': 'ШЈЩҲЩ„',
                'opponent': leader or (f"Щ…ШӘШөШҜШұ {_v33_group_label(slot)}" if slot else 'ЩҠШӘШӯШҜШҜ Щ„Ш§ШӯЩӮЩӢШ§'),
                'fixture': {},
                'team_rank_word': 'ШЈЩҒШ¶Щ„ Ш«Ш§Щ„Ш«',
            }
        except Exception:
            return {'note': 'ШЈЩҒШ¶Щ„ Ш«Ш§Щ„Ш«', 'opponent_group': None, 'opponent': 'ЩҠШӘШӯШҜШҜ ШӯШіШЁ ШӘЩҲШІЩҠШ№ ШЈЩҒШ¶Щ„ Ш§Щ„Ш«ЩҲШ§Щ„Ш«', 'fixture': {}, 'team_rank_word': 'ШЈЩҒШ¶Щ„ Ш«Ш§Щ„Ш«'}
    if pos not in (1, 2):
        return {'note': '-', 'opponent_group': None, 'opponent': 'ЩҠШӘШӯШҜШҜ Щ„Ш§ШӯЩӮЩӢШ§', 'fixture': {}, 'team_rank_word': '-'}
    my_rank_word = 'ШЈЩҲЩ„' if pos == 1 else 'Ш«Ш§ЩҶЩҠ'
    token = f"{my_rank_word} Ш§Щ„Щ…Ш¬Щ…ЩҲШ№Ш© {_v33_group_ar(code)}"
    for m in globals().get('TOURNAMENT_FIXTURES', []) or []:
        if str(m.get('stage')) != 'ШҜЩҲШұ Ш§Щ„ЩҖ32':
            continue
        note = str(m.get('note') or '')
        if token not in note:
            continue
        parts = [p.strip() for p in note.split('Г—')]
        other = ''
        if len(parts) >= 2:
            other = parts[1] if parts[0] == token else parts[0]
        else:
            other = note.replace(token, '').replace('Г—', '').strip()
        opp_rank_word, opp_group = _v38e_parse_group_part(other)
        opponent = _v38d_r32_counterpart_from_note(other, snap) if '_v38d_r32_counterpart_from_note' in globals() else other
        return {
            'note': note,
            'other_part': other,
            'opponent_group': opp_group,
            'opponent_rank_word': opp_rank_word,
            'opponent': opponent,
            'fixture': dict(m),
            'team_rank_word': my_rank_word,
        }
    return {'note': token, 'opponent_group': None, 'opponent': 'ЩҠШӘШӯШҜШҜ ШӯШіШЁ Ш¬ШҜЩҲЩ„ ШҜЩҲШұ Ш§Щ„ЩҖ32', 'fixture': {}, 'team_rank_word': my_rank_word}


def _v38e_match_datetime_line(fixture):
    fixture = fixture or {}
    day = fixture.get('day') or ''
    date = fixture.get('date') or ''
    time = fixture.get('time') or ''
    if day or date or time:
        return f"{day} {date}".strip() + (f" вҖ” {time}" if time else '')
    return "ЩҠШӘШӯШҜШҜ Щ„Ш§ШӯЩӮЩӢШ§"


def _v38e_is_group_complete(code, snap=None):
    snap = snap or _v33_snapshot(False)
    try:
        return len(_v33_group_remaining(code, snap) or []) == 0
    except Exception:
        g = ((snap.get('groups') or {}).get(code, {}) or {})
        return int(g.get('remaining') or 0) == 0


def _v38e_opponent_group_details_text(team):
    team = _v33_find_team(team) or team
    snap = _v33_snapshot(False)
    code, pos, row, rows = _v33_group_row(team, snap)
    info = _v38e_round32_fixture_info_for_team(team, snap)
    opp_group = info.get('opponent_group')
    if not opp_group:
        return (
            f"рҹ“Ҡ ШӘЩҒШ§ШөЩҠЩ„ Щ…Ш¬Щ…ЩҲШ№Ш© Ш§Щ„Ш®ШөЩ… вҖ” {team}\n\n"
            "Щ„Ш§ ЩҠЩ…ЩғЩҶ ШӘШӯШҜЩҠШҜ Щ…Ш¬Щ…ЩҲШ№Ш© Ш§Щ„Ш®ШөЩ… ШӯШӘЩү Ш§Щ„ШўЩҶ.\n\n"
            f"рҹҸҹпёҸ Ш®Ш§ЩҶШ© ШҜЩҲШұ Ш§Щ„ЩҖ32 Ш§Щ„ШӯШ§Щ„ЩҠШ©:\n{info.get('note') or '-'}\n\n"
            f"рҹ“… Щ…ЩҲШ№ШҜ Ш§Щ„Щ…ЩҲШ§Ш¬ЩҮШ©:\n{_v38e_match_datetime_line(info.get('fixture') or {})}"
        )
    opp_rows = (((snap.get('groups') or {}).get(opp_group, {}) or {}).get('rows') or [])
    opponent = info.get('opponent') or 'ЩҠШӘШӯШҜШҜ Щ„Ш§ШӯЩӮЩӢШ§'
    my_rank = info.get('team_rank_word') or _v38d_rank_word(pos)
    opp_rank = info.get('opponent_rank_word') or ''
    lines = [f"рҹ“Ҡ ШӘЩҒШ§ШөЩҠЩ„ Щ…Ш¬Щ…ЩҲШ№Ш© Ш§Щ„Ш®ШөЩ… вҖ” {_v33_group_label(opp_group)}", ""]
    lines.extend(_v38d_group_rows_lines(opp_group, opp_rows) if '_v38d_group_rows_lines' in globals() else [str(opp_rows)])
    lines.append("")
    lines.append("рҹ“… Щ…ШЁШ§ШұЩҠШ§ШӘ Ш§Щ„Щ…Ш¬Щ…ЩҲШ№Ш© Ш§Щ„Щ…ШӘШЁЩӮЩҠШ©:")
    try:
        lines.extend(_v38d_group_remaining_lines(opp_group, snap))
    except Exception:
        lines.append("Щ„Ш§ ШӘЩҲШ¬ШҜ ШЁЩҠШ§ЩҶШ§ШӘ Щ…ШӘШ§ШӯШ©.")
    lines.append("")
    lines.append("рҹҸҹпёҸ ШіШЁШЁ Ш§Щ„Щ…ЩҲШ§Ш¬ЩҮШ©:")
    lines.append(f"{team} ШӘШЈЩҮЩ„ ЩғЩҖ {my_rank} {_v33_group_label(code)}.")
    lines.append("")
    lines.append("ЩҲШЁШӯШіШЁ Ш®Ш§ЩҶШ© ШҜЩҲШұ Ш§Щ„ЩҖ32:")
    lines.append(str(info.get('note') or '-'))
    lines.append("")
    if _v38e_is_group_complete(opp_group, snap):
        lines.append("вң… Ш§Щ„Ш®ШөЩ… ШӯЩҸШіЩ… ШұШіЩ…ЩҠЩӢШ§:")
        lines.append(f"{opponent}" + (f" вҖ” {opp_rank} {_v33_group_label(opp_group)}" if opp_rank else ""))
    else:
        lines.append(f"Щ„Ш°Щ„Щғ {team} ЩҠЩӮШ§ШЁЩ„ ШӯШ§Щ„ЩҠЩӢШ§:")
        lines.append(f"{opponent}" + (f" вҖ” {opp_rank} {_v33_group_label(opp_group)}" if opp_rank else ""))
        lines.append("")
        lines.append(f"вҡ пёҸ ЩӮШҜ ЩҠШӘШәЩҠШұ Ш§Щ„Ш®ШөЩ… ШҘШ°Ш§ ШӘШәЩҠЩ‘Шұ ШӘШұШӘЩҠШЁ {_v33_group_label(opp_group)}.")
    lines.append("")
    lines.append("рҹ“… Щ…ЩҲШ№ШҜ Ш§Щ„Щ…ЩҲШ§Ш¬ЩҮШ©:")
    lines.append(_v38e_match_datetime_line(info.get('fixture') or {}))
    return "\n".join(lines).strip()


def _v38e_has_opponent_group(team):
    try:
        return bool(_v38e_round32_fixture_info_for_team(team, _v33_snapshot(False)).get('opponent_group'))
    except Exception:
        return False


# ---------- ЩғЩҠЩҒ ЩҠШӘШЈЩҮЩ„: ШЈШІШұШ§Шұ Ш§Щ„Щ…ШӘШЈЩҮЩ„ ШұШіЩ…ЩҠЩӢШ§ ШӘШҙЩ…Щ„ ШӘЩҒШ§ШөЩҠЩ„ Щ…Ш¬Щ…ЩҲШ№Ш© Ш§Щ„Ш®ШөЩ… ----------
def _v33_how_qualify_keyboard(team):
    team = _v33_find_team(team) or team
    snap = _v33_snapshot(False)
    code, pos, row, rows = _v33_group_row(team, snap)
    status_txt = (snap.get('status') or {}).get(team, '')
    key = _v33_team_button_key(team)
    if _v38d_is_official_qualified(status_txt) or _v38d_is_official_out(status_txt):
        btns = []
        if _v38d_is_official_qualified(status_txt) and _v38e_has_opponent_group(team):
            btns.append([InlineKeyboardButton("рҹ“Ҡ ШӘЩҒШ§ШөЩҠЩ„ Щ…Ш¬Щ…ЩҲШ№Ш© Ш§Щ„Ш®ШөЩ…", callback_data=f"v32|opp_group|{key}")])
        btns.append([InlineKeyboardButton("рҹ“Ҡ ШӘЩҒШ§ШөЩҠЩ„ Ш§Щ„Щ…Ш¬Щ…ЩҲШ№Ш©", callback_data=f"v32|how_group|{key}")])
        btns.append([InlineKeyboardButton("в¬…пёҸ ШұШ¬ЩҲШ№", callback_data="mainmenu|home")])
        return InlineKeyboardMarkup(btns)
    possible, _examples = _v38d_possible_positions(team, snap)
    rows_btn = []
    row_btn = []
    if 1 in possible:
        row_btn.append(InlineKeyboardButton("рҹҘҮ Ш§ШӯШӘЩ…Ш§Щ„Ш§ШӘ Ш§Щ„Щ…ШұЩғШІ Ш§Щ„ШЈЩҲЩ„", callback_data=f"v32|how_first|{key}"))
    if 2 in possible:
        row_btn.append(InlineKeyboardButton("рҹҘҲ Ш§ШӯШӘЩ…Ш§Щ„Ш§ШӘ Ш§Щ„Щ…ШұЩғШІ Ш§Щ„Ш«Ш§ЩҶЩҠ", callback_data=f"v32|how_second|{key}"))
    if row_btn:
        rows_btn.append(row_btn[:2])
    row_btn = []
    if 3 in possible:
        row_btn.append(InlineKeyboardButton("рҹҘү Ш§ШӯШӘЩ…Ш§Щ„Ш§ШӘ ШЈЩҒШ¶Щ„ Ш«Ш§Щ„Ш«", callback_data=f"v32|how_thirds|{key}"))
        row_btn.append(InlineKeyboardButton("рҹҸҹпёҸ Ш§Щ„Ш®ШөЩҲЩ… Ш§Щ„Щ…ШӯШӘЩ…Щ„ЩҠЩҶ", callback_data=f"v32|opp_all|{key}"))
        rows_btn.append(row_btn)
    rows_btn.append([InlineKeyboardButton("рҹ“Ҡ ШӘЩҒШ§ШөЩҠЩ„ Ш§Щ„Щ…Ш¬Щ…ЩҲШ№Ш©", callback_data=f"v32|how_group|{key}")])
    rows_btn.append([InlineKeyboardButton("рҹ§® Ш¬ШұЩ‘ШЁ ШіЩҠЩҶШ§ШұЩҠЩҲ", callback_data="v32|calc_start"), InlineKeyboardButton("в¬…пёҸ ШұШ¬ЩҲШ№", callback_data="mainmenu|home")])
    return InlineKeyboardMarkup(rows_btn)


# ---------- ШЈЩҒШ¶Щ„ Ш§Щ„Ш«ЩҲШ§Щ„Ш«: ШӘШөЩҶЩҠЩҒ ШөШӯЩҠШӯ ----------
def _v38e_third_categories(team, target_pts, snap=None):
    snap = snap or _v33_snapshot(False)
    team = _v33_find_team(team) or team
    my_code = _v33_team_group(team)
    safe, compare_only, danger_only, mixed = [], [], [], []
    for code, _teams in WORLD_CUP_GROUPS:
        if code == my_code:
            continue
        tr = _v33_third_row_for_group(code, snap)
        if not tr:
            continue
        third_team = tr.get('team') or '-'
        pts = _v37_safe_int(tr.get('Pts'))
        played = _v37_safe_int(tr.get('P'))
        gd = _v37_safe_int(tr.get('GD'))
        current_max = _v37_team_max_from_row(tr)
        max_third = _v37_max_third_points_for_group(code, snap)
        can_equal = pts <= int(target_pts) <= current_max
        can_exceed = current_max > int(target_pts)
        obj = {
            'group': code, 'team': third_team, 'pts': pts, 'played': played, 'gd': gd,
            'current_max': current_max, 'max_third': max_third,
            'can_equal': bool(can_equal), 'can_exceed': bool(can_exceed),
            'match': _v37_remaining_match_short_for_team(third_team, code, snap),
        }
        if current_max < int(target_pts) and max_third < int(target_pts):
            safe.append(obj)
        elif can_exceed and can_equal:
            mixed.append(obj)
        elif can_exceed:
            danger_only.append(obj)
        elif can_equal:
            compare_only.append(obj)
        else:
            safe.append(obj)
    key_d = lambda x: (-x['current_max'], -x['pts'], x['group'])
    danger_only.sort(key=key_d); mixed.sort(key=key_d)
    compare_only.sort(key=lambda x: (-x['pts'], -x['gd'], x['group']))
    safe.sort(key=lambda x: (-x['pts'], -x['gd'], x['group']))
    return danger_only, mixed, compare_only, safe


def _v37_third_categories(team, target_pts, snap=None):
    # ШӘЩҲШ§ЩҒЩӮ Щ…Ш№ Ш§Щ„ШҜЩҲШ§Щ„ Ш§Щ„ЩӮШҜЩҠЩ…Ш©: danger = ШӘШ¬Ш§ЩҲШІ + Щ…Ш®ШӘЩ„Ш·ШҢ compare = Щ…ЩӮШ§ШұЩҶШ© ЩҒЩӮШ·ШҢ safe = Щ…Ш¶Щ…ЩҲЩҶ.
    danger, mixed, compare, safe = _v38e_third_categories(team, target_pts, snap)
    return danger + mixed, compare, safe


def _v38e_third_item_line(x, target_pts, team, mode):
    g = _v33_group_label(x['group'])
    base = f"- {x['team']} вҖ” {g} | Щ„Ш№ШЁ: {x['played']}/3 | {x['pts']} ЩҶЩӮШ§Ш· | ЩҒШ§ШұЩӮ {x['gd']:+d}"
    if mode == 'danger':
        note = f"ЩӮШҜ ЩҠШӘШ¬Ш§ЩҲШІ {team} ШҘШ°Ш§ ЩҲШөЩ„ ШҘЩ„Щү ШЈЩғШ«Шұ Щ…ЩҶ {target_pts} ЩҶЩӮШ§Ш·."
    elif mode == 'mixed':
        note = f"Ш§Щ„ЩҒЩҲШІ ЩӮШҜ ЩҠШ¬Ш№Щ„ЩҮ ЩҠШӘШ¬Ш§ЩҲШІ {team}ШҢ ЩҲШ§Щ„ШӘШ№Ш§ШҜЩ„/ШіЩҠЩҶШ§ШұЩҠЩҲ Ш§Щ„ЩҶЩӮШ§Ш· ЩӮШҜ ЩҠШҜШ®Щ„ЩҮ Щ…ЩӮШ§ШұЩҶШ© Ш§Щ„ЩҒШ§ШұЩӮ ШҘШ°Ш§ ЩҲШөЩ„ ШҘЩ„Щү {target_pts} ЩҶЩӮШ§Ш·."
    elif mode == 'compare':
        note = f"ШҘШ°Ш§ ЩҲШөЩ„ ШҘЩ„Щү {target_pts} ЩҶЩӮШ§Ш· ЩҠШҜШ®Щ„ Щ…ЩӮШ§ШұЩҶШ© Ш§Щ„ЩҒШ§ШұЩӮ Щ…Ш№ {team}."
    else:
        note = f"Щ„Ш§ ЩҠШіШӘШ·ЩҠШ№ Ш§Щ„ЩҲШөЩҲЩ„ ШҘЩ„Щү {target_pts} ЩҶЩӮШ§Ш·ШҢ Щ„Ш°Щ„Щғ ЩҠШЁЩӮЩү Ш®Щ„ЩҒ {team}."
    if x.get('match') and mode != 'safe':
        note += f" Ш§Щ„Щ…ШЁШ§ШұШ§Ш© Ш§Щ„Щ…ШӨШ«ШұШ©: {x['match']}."
    return base + "\n  " + note


def _v37_one_line_item(x, target_pts, team, mode):
    return _v38e_third_item_line(x, target_pts, team, mode)


def _v37_third_path_summary_block(team, target_pts, snap=None):
    danger, mixed, compare, safe = _v38e_third_categories(team, target_pts, snap)
    guaranteed = len(safe)
    lines = []
    lines.append(f"вң… Ш№ШҜШҜ Ш§Щ„Ш«ЩҲШ§Щ„Ш« Ш§Щ„Щ…Ш¶Щ…ЩҲЩҶ ЩҲШ¬ЩҲШҜЩҮЩ… Ш®Щ„ЩҒ {team}: {min(guaranteed,4)}/4")
    if guaranteed >= 4:
        lines.append("Ш§Щ„ШӯШ§Щ„Ш©: вң… ШӘШЈЩҮЩ„ ШұШіЩ…ЩҠ Ш¶Щ…ЩҶ ШЈЩҒШ¶Щ„ Ш§Щ„Ш«ЩҲШ§Щ„Ш« ШҘШ°Ш§ ШЈЩҶЩҮЩү Ш§Щ„Щ…ЩҶШӘШ®ШЁ Щ…Ш¬Щ…ЩҲШ№ШӘЩҮ Ш«Ш§Щ„Ш«ЩӢШ§ ШЁЩҮШ°Ш§ Ш§Щ„ШұШөЩҠШҜ.")
    else:
        lines.append(f"Ш§Щ„ШӯШ§Щ„Ш©: ЩҠШӯШӘШ§Ш¬ {4-guaranteed} Щ…ЩҶШӘШ®ШЁШ§ШӘ Ш«Ш§Щ„Ш«Ш© ШҘШ¶Ш§ЩҒЩҠШ© ШӘШЁЩӮЩү Ш®Щ„ЩҒЩҮ Щ„Ш¶Щ…Ш§ЩҶ Ш§Щ„ШӘШЈЩҮЩ„.")
    lines.append("")
    if danger:
        lines.append(f"рҹ”Ҙ Щ…Щ…ЩғЩҶ ЩҠШӘШ¬Ш§ЩҲШІ {team}:")
        for x in danger[:7]:
            lines.append(_v38e_third_item_line(x, target_pts, team, 'danger'))
        lines.append("")
    if mixed:
        lines.append("вҡ пёҸ ЩӮШҜ ЩҠШӘШ¬Ш§ЩҲШІ ШЈЩҲ ЩҠШҜШ®Щ„ Щ…ЩӮШ§ШұЩҶШ© Ш§Щ„ЩҒШ§ШұЩӮ:")
        for x in mixed[:7]:
            lines.append(_v38e_third_item_line(x, target_pts, team, 'mixed'))
        lines.append("")
    if compare:
        lines.append("вҡ–пёҸ ЩҠШҜШ®Щ„ Щ…ЩӮШ§ШұЩҶШ© Ш§Щ„ЩҒШ§ШұЩӮ:")
        for x in compare[:7]:
            lines.append(_v38e_third_item_line(x, target_pts, team, 'compare'))
        lines.append("")
    if safe:
        lines.append(f"вң… Ш®Щ„ЩҒ {team} Щ…Ш¶Щ…ЩҲЩҶ:")
        for x in safe[:6]:
            lines.append(_v38e_third_item_line(x, target_pts, team, 'safe'))
        lines.append("")
    return lines


# ---------- Щ…ШЁШ§ШҙШұ Ш§Щ„Щ…ШЁШ§ШұШ§Ш©: scoring plays Ш§Щ„ШұШіЩ…ЩҠШ© ЩҒЩӮШ· ----------
def _v38e_node_text_blob(x):
    vals = []
    def add(v):
        if v is not None:
            vals.append(str(v))
    if isinstance(x, dict):
        for k in ['text', 'shortText', 'displayText', 'description', 'headline', 'summary', 'playText']:
            add(x.get(k))
        typ = x.get('type')
        if isinstance(typ, dict):
            for k in ['text','description','displayName','name','abbreviation']:
                add(typ.get(k))
    return ' '.join(vals)


def _v38e_names_from_node(x):
    names = []
    if not isinstance(x, dict):
        return names
    def clean(n):
        try:
            return _v43_clean_person_name(n)
        except Exception:
            return str(n or '').strip()
    for k in ['scorer', 'athlete', 'player', 'participant']:
        v = x.get(k)
        if isinstance(v, dict):
            n = clean(v.get('displayName') or v.get('shortName') or v.get('fullName') or v.get('name'))
            if n: names.append(n)
    for k in ['athletes', 'players', 'participants', 'athletesInvolved']:
        arr = x.get(k)
        if isinstance(arr, list):
            for it in arr:
                if isinstance(it, dict):
                    role = str(it.get('type') or it.get('role') or it.get('category') or '').lower()
                    a = it.get('athlete') if isinstance(it.get('athlete'), dict) else it
                    n = clean(a.get('displayName') or a.get('shortName') or a.get('fullName') or a.get('name'))
                    if n and ('scorer' in role or 'goal' in role):
                        names.insert(0, n)
                    elif n:
                        names.append(n)
    out=[]
    for n in names:
        if n and n not in out:
            out.append(n)
    return out


def _v38e_name_from_scoring_node(x):
    blob = _v38e_node_text_blob(x)
    # ШЈЩҲЩ„ЩӢШ§ Щ…ЩҶ Ш§Щ„ЩҶШө Ш§Щ„ШұШіЩ…ЩҠ ШҘШ°Ш§ ЩғШ§ЩҶ ЩҲШ§Ш¶ШӯЩӢШ§.
    try:
        n = _v43_extract_goal_name_from_text(blob)
        if n:
            return n
    except Exception:
        pass
    names = _v38e_names_from_node(x)
    if not names:
        return ''
    # ШҘШ°Ш§ ЩҒЩҠЩҮ ШЈЩғШ«Шұ Щ…ЩҶ Ш§ШіЩ…ШҢ Ш§Ш®ШӘШұ Ш§Щ„Ш§ШіЩ… Ш§Щ„Щ…ЩҲШ¬ЩҲШҜ ШЁЩҲШ¶ЩҲШӯ ЩҒЩҠ ЩҶШө Ш§Щ„ШӯШҜШ« ЩӮШЁЩ„ ШәЩҠШұЩҮ.
    low = blob.lower()
    for n in names:
        if n.lower() in low:
            return n
    return names[0]


def _v38e_minute_from_node(x):
    blob = _v38e_node_text_blob(x)
    try:
        return _v43_minute_from_node(x, blob)
    except Exception:
        pass
    m = re.search(r"([1-9][0-9]{0,2}(?:\+[0-9]{1,2})?)\s*['вҖҷ]", blob)
    return m.group(1) if m else ''


def _v38e_collect_scoring_nodes(data):
    # ШҘШ°Ш§ ESPN ШЈШ№Ш·Щү scoringPlays Ш¬Ш§ЩҮШІШ©ШҢ ЩҶШіШӘШ®ШҜЩ…ЩҮШ§ ЩҒЩӮШ· ЩҲЩҶЩҲЩӮЩҒШҢ Щ„ШЈЩҶЩҮШ§ Ш§Щ„Щ…ШөШҜШұ Ш§Щ„ШұШіЩ…ЩҠ.
    direct = []
    def scan_for_key(obj):
        if isinstance(obj, dict):
            sp = obj.get('scoringPlays') or obj.get('scoringplays')
            if isinstance(sp, list) and sp:
                direct.extend([x for x in sp if isinstance(x, dict)])
            for v in obj.values():
                scan_for_key(v)
        elif isinstance(obj, list):
            for it in obj:
                scan_for_key(it)
    scan_for_key(data)
    if direct:
        return direct
    nodes = []
    def walk(obj):
        if isinstance(obj, dict):
            score_value = obj.get('scoreValue')
            scoring_play = obj.get('scoringPlay') is True or obj.get('scoringplay') is True
            typ = obj.get('type')
            type_id = ''
            if isinstance(typ, dict):
                type_id = str(typ.get('id') or typ.get('abbreviation') or typ.get('text') or '')
            # ESPN soccer goals ШәШ§Щ„ШЁЩӢШ§ scoringPlay/scoreValue. Щ„Ш§ ЩҶШіШӘШ®ШҜЩ… ШЈЩҠ ШӯШҜШ« Щ„Щ…Ш¬ШұШҜ ЩҲШ¬ЩҲШҜ ЩғЩ„Щ…Ш© Goal.
            if scoring_play or str(score_value) in ('1', '1.0') or type_id in ('70',):
                nodes.append(obj)
            for v in obj.values():
                walk(v)
        elif isinstance(obj, list):
            for it in obj:
                walk(it)
    walk(data)
    return nodes


def _v38e_extract_scorers_from_summary_json(data, debug=None):
    debug = debug if debug is not None else []
    nodes = _v38e_collect_scoring_nodes(data)
    out = []
    for x in nodes:
        name = _v38e_name_from_scoring_node(x)
        if not name:
            continue
        blob = _v38e_node_text_blob(x)
        own = bool(re.search(r'own goal', blob, re.I))
        pen = bool(re.search(r'penalty', blob, re.I))
        minute = _v38e_minute_from_node(x)
        try:
            line = _v43_format_goal_line(name, minute, own=own, pen=pen)
        except Exception:
            line = name
        if line:
            out.append(line)
    # Щ„Ш§ ЩҶШІЩҠЩ„ Ш§Щ„ШӘЩғШұШ§Шұ Щ„ЩҶЩҒШі Ш§Щ„Щ„Ш§Ш№ШЁ ШҘШ°Ш§ ШіШ¬Щ„ ЩҮШҜЩҒЩҠЩҶШӣ ЩҒЩӮШ· ЩҶШІЩҠЩ„ Ш§Щ„ШӘЩғШұШ§Шұ Ш§Щ„Щ…Ш·Ш§ШЁЩӮ Щ„ЩҶЩҒШі Ш§Щ„ЩҮШҜЩҒ/Ш§Щ„ШҜЩӮЩҠЩӮШ©.
    clean, seen = [], set()
    for s in out:
        key = re.sub(r'\s+', ' ', str(s).lower()).strip()
        if key and key not in seen:
            seen.add(key); clean.append(s)
    debug.append(f'V38E strict scoring plays: {len(clean)}')
    return clean[:12]

_v43_extract_scorers_from_summary_json = _v38e_extract_scorers_from_summary_json
_v48_extract_scorers_from_summary_json = _v38e_extract_scorers_from_summary_json


